- Added the default ReAct agent harness for autonomous in-agent tool/delegation loops, including max-step enforcement, Scratchpad audit, per-tool call limits, similar-query warnings, concurrent-safe tool execution, bounded context compaction, and compatibility switches for single-shot and caller-planned tool execution.
